}
```

**Fix:** Only enqueue the system event if `deliver` wasn't explicitly set to `false`:
```typescript
if (!result.delivered && value.deliver !== false) {
  enqueueSystemEvent(`${prefix}: ${summary}`.trim(), {
    sessionKey: mainSessionKey,
  });
  if (value.wakeMode === "now") {
    requestHeartbeatNow({ reason: `hook:${jobId}` });
  }
}
```

The `value.deliver` is already part of the `HookAgentDispatchPayload` type and is set by the idler's dispatch call. This is a one-line condition change.

